## MIYOI'S GEIDONTEI INN
*"Come in, sit down. First drink's on me while you figure out what you need."*

**Operator:** Miyoi Okunoda

The social heart of the hub. Miyoi runs a clean, welcoming establishment. She is an excellent listener and a natural peacemaker. She also occasionally serves phantom customers, which she handles without comment.

**Room Options:**
| Room | Cost | Benefit |
|---|---|---|
| Basic Room | 5gp | Standard long rest |
| Premium Room | 200gp | Long rest + one Inspiration die usable next session *(Locked)* |
| Shrine Room | 300gp | Long rest + advantage on next saving throw vs. curse or charm *(Locked)* |

**Meals:**
| Meal | Effect | Price |
|---|---|---|
| Standard Meal | No mechanical effect | 5sp |
| Hearty Meal | Remove one level of exhaustion | 3gp |
| Miyoi's Special | DM discretion | Ask |

**Notes:**
- Miyoi remembers every regular and what they usually order
- Local gossip flows freely at the bar — conversations here may yield rumors (DM discretion)